                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.00119 Council/9–745: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Ambassador in Iran</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Murray</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-09-13T19:00:00-04:00"
                            >September 13, 1945—7 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>521. Urtel 702, Sept 7. Dept has communicated Iranian Govt’s views to Secretary
                    in London, on basis of similar representations made by Iranian Legation in
                    Washington.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
